POTD-#79
TASK-2-Sum of Array
APPROACH-(RECUSRION)
1.)Simply start from last element and add  element in first element and then recursively call function for next element to add.
SOLUTION-
//User function template for C++
class Solution{
public:
	// function to return sum of elements
	// in an array of size n
	int sum(int arr[], int n) {
	    // code here
	     // ans=0;
	    if(n==1)
	    return arr[0];
	   arr[0]+=arr[n-1];
	    return sum(arr,n-1);
	}
};
TIME COMPLEXITY-
O(N)
SPACE COMPLEXITY-
O(N)
